// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2013 — Mass File Rename (ransomhub)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 82ac9ab4-2a29-5690-8595-81678d3dfbc9

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
